snippet.title: SEE YOU... Game Boy Color Homebrew Horror
snippet.description:
Worried about your friend, you stop by his apartment to check in on him...only to discover he's nowhere to be seen and the apartment is barricaded and bloodied.


See You... is a horror-themed Game Boy Color point & click prototype that lasts only a few minutes. It's my very first "finished" experience, with all pixel art inside having been hand drawn!
